<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Missing Vehicle Report</title>
</head>

<body>

    <img src="/images/government_of_india.jpg" height="100px">
    <img src="/images/mh_police.jpg" height="100px">

    <h2>Missing Vehicle Report Form / हरवलेल्या वाहनाचा तक्रार फॉर्म</h2>

    <form method="post" action="/Cyber_Crime" enctype="multipart/form-data">
       <h3>Owner Information / मालकाची माहिती</h3>
        
        <input name="name" placeholder="Owner Name / मालकाचे नाव" required /><br><br>
        
        <input name="mobile" placeholder="Contact Number / संपर्क क्रमांक" required /><br><br>
        
        <textarea name="address" placeholder="Owner Address / मालकाचा पत्ता" required></textarea><br><br>
          <h3>Vehicle Details / वाहनाची माहिती</h3>
        
        <select name="vehicleType" required>
            <option value="">Select Vehicle Type / वाहनाचा प्रकार निवडा</option>
            <option value="car">Car / कार</option>
            <option value="bike">Motorcycle / मोटारसायकल</option>
            <option value="scooter">Scooter / स्कूटर</option>
            <option value="auto">Auto Rickshaw / ऑटो रिक्षा</option>
            <option value="commercial">Commercial Vehicle / व्यावसायिक वाहन</option>
            <option value="other">Other / इतर</option>
        </select><br><br>

<input name="otherVehicleType" placeholder="If other, please specify / इतर असल्यास कृपया स्पष्ट करा"><br><br>
        
        <input name="vehicleNumber" placeholder="Vehicle Number / वाहन क्रमांक" required /><br><br>
        
        <input name="vehicleMake" placeholder="Make (Brand) / ब्रँड" required /><br><br>
        
        <input name="vehicleModel" placeholder="Model / मॉडेल" required /><br><br>
        
        <input name="vehicleColor" placeholder="Color / रंग" required /><br><br>
        
      

        <h3>Missing Details / हरवण्याची माहिती</h3>
        
        <input name="location" placeholder="Last Parked Location / शेवटचे पार्क केलेले ठिकाण" required /><br><br>
  <input name="dateTime" type="datetime-local" required /><br><br>
        
        <textarea name="circumstances" placeholder="Circumstances of Theft / चोरीची परिस्थिती" required></textarea><br><br>

        <h3>Additional Information / अतिरिक्त माहिती</h3>
<small>Vehicle Photo (Required) / वाहनाचा फोटो (आवश्यक):</small><br>
 <input type="file" name="vehiclePhoto" accept="image/*" required /><br><br>
  <small>RC / Passing Bill from RTO Office (Required) / आरटीओ कार्यालयातील आरसी/पासिंग बील (आवश्यक):</small><br>
   <input type="file" name="rcPassingBill" accept="image/*,.pdf" required /><br><br>

 <small>Insurance Copy (Optional) / विमा कॉपी (पर्यायी):</small><br>
<input type="file" name="insuranceCopy" accept="image/*,.pdf" /><br><br>
 <textarea name="additionalInfo" placeholder="Any Additional Information / कोणतीही अतिरिक्त माहिती"></textarea><br><br>

        <button type="submit">Submit Report / अहवाल सादर करा</button></form>

</body>
</html>
